casebody.data:
No. 84,

Orig.

United States v. Alaska. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 474 U. S. 1044.]

Report of the Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions to the Report, with supporting briefs, not to exceed 75 pages, may be filed within 75 days. Replies, if any, not to exceed 75 pages, may be filed within 60 days after receipt of the other party’s exceptions. Sur-reply briefs, if any, not to exceed 30 pages, may be filed within 30 days after receipt of the other party’s reply.
